        "Keywords" = "8:"
        "ARPCOMMENTS" = "8:NetVoyager is a lightweight network diagnostics app that lets users quickly assess connectivity and trace routes. With built-in ping and traceroute tools, it helps identify latency issues, unreachable hosts, and visualize packet paths. Ideal for IT pros, engineers, and curious users, with a clean UI and real-time results."
